children.text: 43 North is a full service restaurant offering casual lunch fair. Featured items include Jerk chicken sandwich, french onion soup & nicoise salad
The Sugarhouse is a quick service restaurant offering multiple station mid-mountain. Featured items include ramen station and BBQ.
The Summit Lodge is a quick service restaurant offering soups, burgers, mediterranean food and a full service bar. Featured items include gyro's and bowls.
The Sitting Bull is a full service restaurant offering classic American pub food. Featured items include wings, nachos, toasted sandwiches and salads.
The Round House is a quick service restaurant offering multiple food stations. Featured items include pizza, tacos, burgers, fresh made salads & breakfast items.
Coleman Brook Tavern is a full service restaurant offering casual American fair. Featured items include short ribs, hearty sandwiches, and speciality entrees.
Base 68 is a quick service restaurant offering beer, brats & pretzels. Featured items include local craft beers.
The Coffee Exchange is a coffee bar in our Solitude lobby offering Lavazza hot drinks. Featuring fresh pastries
Base 68 is a quick service restaurant offering grab and go comfort food . Featured items include selection of burgers, soups and salads.
